0:02:48.92,000 --> 0:02:5,000
Nature has evolved over 3.8 billion years

49
0:02:51.84,000 --> 0:02:52,000
to be able to do this,

50
0:02:53.72,000 --> 0:02:55,000
but now through the use of synthetic biology,

51
