0:03:20.24,000 --> 0:03:23,000
and even sequester renewable energy from algae.

59
0:03:24.84,000 --> 0:03:28,000
To think about how we might access this inherent brilliance of nature --

60
0:03:29.68,000 --> 0:03:31,000
